TextEng: You're better off dead, you freak!
I'll leave you alone then. Goodbye!
You just have to get to a safe place. Do you know one?
Text: 안전한 곳으로 가기만 하면 돼. 어디 아는 곳 있어?

TextEng: It's okay. Follow me and we'll go someplace safe.
Text: 괜찮아. 날 따라와, 안전한 곳으로 가자.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start>> Settle down now, I don't mean you any harm.
Just stay here where you won't hurt yourself!
Okay, you runs to Helmite sanctu-thingy.
Text: 좋아, 너 헬름의 성소-뭐시기 로 달려.

TextEng: Look, do you know a safe place to go?
Text: 그러니까, 갈 만한 안전한 곳을 아나?

TextEng: Look, just follow me and you'll be fine, all right?
Text: 있지, 그냥 날 따라오면 괜찮을 거야. 알겠지?

TextEng: You'll be fine. Just stay here out of trouble.
Text: 넌 괜찮을 거야. 문제 생기지 않게 여기 가만히 있어.

TextEng: You just stays here, so you not get hurt.
Text: 너 그냥 여기 있어. 그러면 안 다쳐.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You settle now. Me not hurt you. Honest.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 이제 진정해. 나 너 안 해쳐. 진짜야.

TextEng: You know about zombies at all?
Shhh... relax. I'm <Race> just like you. Trust me.
Be still. I'm <race>, like you. Not undead.
Shut up, you! No way for <race> folk to act!
Text: 닥쳐! <race> 족속이 그렇게 행동하는 게 아냐!

TextEng: Me <race> kind, like you. Be quiet.
Shut up! That's not the <race> way to act!
You know safe place to run?
Follow and me lead you to safe place.
You runs to Shining Serpent then.
You stay here away from trouble, okay?
Text: 너 여기 있어. 문제 안 생기게, 알지?

TextEng: Do you know anything about the zombies?
You knows a safe place for you to go?
Okay, just go to the Shining Serpent.
You're okay. Just get to the Helmite Sanctuary.
Text: 넌 괜찮아. 헬름의 성소로 가기만 해.

TextEng: Me leave then. Bye.
Me just kill you! Too loud!
Text: 나 그냥 너 죽여! 너무 시끄러워!

TextEng: You okay. Me <race> kind just like yous.
Just follows me and you be okay, yuh?
Text: 그냥 날 따라와. 그럼 괜찮아, 응?
